name: Wookiee
Lore: 'Wookiees are known to be fierce warriors. Combine high technology with a primitive lifestyle. Escaped Imperial slavery after the Battle of Endor.',
Text: 'Power +1 at a jungle, forest or Kashyyyk site. Also power +1 at same site as any Imperial. Wookiee Strangle is a Used Interrupt. When Bowcaster is deployed on or fired by this Wookiee, X=1. Adds 3 to destiny of each of your bowcasters.',
